MODIFICATIONS NOTICE:

ForgeFox has made the following substantial modifications to the original
Roo Code codebase:

1. Complete rebranding from "Roo Code" to "ForgeFox"
2. Removal of dependencies on Roo Code cloud services (authentication,
   telemetry, cloud API proxy)
3. Replacement of all logo and icon assets
4. Renaming of VS Code extension identifiers, command IDs, configuration
   keys, and package namespaces
5. Disabling of proprietary cloud features (Roo Code Cloud, Roo Code
   Router) that depended on roocode.com infrastructure
6. Ongoing development focused on local-first, provider-agnostic AI
   coding assistance

